00:11:36.063 --> 00:11:37.532 position:21% line:89% align:start
Well, why should you?

00:11:37.666 --> 00:11:40.434 position:13% line:83% align:start
My son's now bereft of his
memory and demonic powers,

00:11:40.569 --> 00:11:42.269 position:13% line:89% align:start
and no longer a demon lord.

00:11:42.403 --> 00:11:44.104 position:21% line:83% align:start
Thus, I will separate
him from demons

00:11:44.238 --> 00:11:46.407 position:24% line:83% align:start
and have him start
over as a human.

00:11:46.541 --> 00:11:48.475 position:13% line:83% align:start
This is the perfect chance
for him to become

00:11:48.610 --> 00:11:50.110 position:27% line:89% align:start
