00:11:54.315 --> 00:11:56.551 position:24% line:83% align:start
I beg your pardon,
Your Imperial Majesty,

00:11:56.685 --> 00:11:58.752 position:24% line:83% align:start
but what about your
son's arranged marriage

00:11:58.886 --> 00:12:00.187 position:27% line:89% align:start
with my daughter?

00:12:00.321 --> 00:12:02.790 position:19% line:83% align:start
Do be at ease, I don't
plan to cancel it now.

00:12:02.923 --> 00:12:06.595 position:13% line:83% align:start
I will seek a suitable time
and reason for the annulment.

00:12:06.727 --> 00:12:07.728 position:21% line:89% align:start
Without our consent?

00:12:07.861 --> 00:12:09.396 position:27% line:89% align:start
That is not fair!

00:12:09.531 --> 00:12:11.966 position:10% line:83% align:start
There's hope yet for Claude
despite this setback of his.

00:12:12.099 --> 00:12:14.902 position:21% line:83% align:start
He has the option to
reconsider his future now.

00:12:15.035 --> 00:12:16.971 position:19% line:83% align:start
I am certain there will
be plenty of candidates

00:12:17.104 --> 00:12:19.073 position:5% line:89% align:start
who hope to wed him as a human.

00:12:20.341 --> 00:12:21.576 position:33% line:89% align:start
Aileen, yes?

00:12:21.710 --> 00:12:24.646 position:13% line:83% align:start
What a pleasure to finally
make your acquaintance.

00:12:24.778 --> 00:12:26.814 position:21% line:83% align:start
I pray you are well,
Dowager Empress.

00:12:26.947 --> 00:12:28.749 position:10% line:89% align:start
And the pleasure is all mine.

00:12:28.882 --> 00:12:30.217 position:30% line:89% align:start
[LARA chuckles]

00:12:30.351 --> 00:12:32.621 position:16% line:83% align:start
Well, aren't you a polite
and endearing young lady!

00:12:32.753 --> 00:12:34.689 position:21% line:89% align:start
I feel a bit jealous.

00:12:34.822 --> 00:12:36.591 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
If the accounts are true,

00:12:36.725 --> 00:12:39.193 position:5% line:89% align:start
this woman's over 60 years old!

00:12:39.326 --> 00:12:41.028 position:21% line:83% align:start
[LARA] As it just so
happens, I plan to host

00:12:41.161 --> 00:12:42.429 position:21% line:89% align:start
an extravagant ball,

00:12:42.564 --> 00:12:44.098 position:24% line:83% align:start
and it would be the
perfect opportunity

00:12:44.231 --> 00:12:46.133 position:21% line:83% align:start
for my dear grandson
to choose a future wife

00:12:46.267 --> 00:12:48.202 position:24% line:83% align:start
who is suitable for
his new lifestyle.

00:12:48.335 --> 00:12:50.538 position:24% line:83% align:start
I never cease to be
impressed by your astute

00:12:50.672 --> 00:12:54.108 position:19% line:83% align:start
