00:12:58.412 --> 00:13:00.515 position:24% line:83% align:start
My, there must have
been an oversight.

00:13:00.649 --> 00:13:02.316 position:19% line:83% align:start
Wouldn't it cause more
trouble for your family

00:13:02.449 --> 00:13:04.586 position:16% line:83% align:start
to receive an invitation
at this late date?

00:13:04.719 --> 00:13:07.888 position:10% line:83% align:start
But I am still Lord Claude's
fiancÃ©e, Your Majesty!

00:13:08.022 --> 00:13:09.990 position:19% line:83% align:start
