worry your pretty little head,

00:13:12.459 --> 00:13:13.695 position:38% line:89% align:start
my dear.

00:13:13.827 --> 00:13:15.597 position:13% line:83% align:start
CÃ©dric and Lilia are taking
care of him quite well

00:13:15.730 --> 00:13:17.131 position:33% line:89% align:start
without you.

00:13:17.264 --> 00:13:19.567 position:16% line:83% align:start
Allow me to confirm Lord
Claude's health for myself.

00:13:19.701 --> 00:13:20.968 position:24% line:89% align:start
Please, just once!

00:13:21.101 --> 00:13:22.671 position:19% line:83% align:start
I beg of you, at least
allow me this much

00:13:22.803 --> 00:13:23.871 position:30% line:89% align:start
as his fiancÃ©e!

00:13:24.004 --> 00:13:25.640 position:41% line:83% align:start
[LARA]
How unseemly.

00:13:25.774 --> 00:13:29.443 position:7% line:83% align:start
If you do love him as you say,
shouldn't you let him go?

00:13:33.881 --> 00:13:35.949 position:13% line:89% align:start
Pardon me for interrupting.

00:13:36.083 --> 00:13:38.252 position:21% line:89% align:start
Lilia was insistent.

00:13:38.385 --> 00:13:40.555 position:27% line:83% align:start
Oh, Grandmother,
this is far too cruel!

00:13:40.689 --> 00:13:43.558 position:10% line:83% align:start
You mustn't force Lady Aileen
to break up with him!

00:13:43.692 --> 00:13:44.626 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Lilia!

00:13:44.759 --> 00:13:46.293 position:10% line:89% align:start
What is this woman plotting?

00:13:46.427 --> 00:13:48.162 position:24% line:83% align:start
It would be rather
suspicious to annul

00:13:48.295 --> 00:13:51.098 position:21% line:83% align:start
the engagement after
he lost his memory.

00:13:51.231 --> 00:13:53.233 position:21% line:83% align:start
The two of them have
developed quite the reputation

00:13:53.367 --> 00:13:55.737 position:30% line:83% align:start
for being in a
close relationship.

00:13:55.869 --> 00:13:57.404 position:27% line:89% align:start
They're a couple!

00:13:57.539 --> 00:14:00.608 position:5% line:83% align:start
So we should at least invite her
to the ball, right, Grandmother?

00:14:00.742 --> 00:14:01.676 position:33% line:89% align:start
[LARA sighs]

00:14:01.810 --> 00:14:03.110 position:10% line:89% align:start
The two of you have a point.

00:14:03.243 --> 00:14:05.580 position:21% line:83% align:start
I suppose I can send
an invitation to her.

00:14:05.714 --> 00:14:08.349 position:24% line:83% align:start
However, should you
try otherwise to meet

00:14:08.482 --> 00:14:09.818 position:27% line:89% align:start
with Lord Claude,

00:14:09.950 --> 00:14:13.187 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'll have you beheaded for going
against an imperial decree.

00:14:16.524 --> 00:14:17.625 position:35% line:89% align:start
Good luck.

00:14:17.759 --> 00:14:19.193 position:16% line:83% align:start
I very much look forward
to seeing what you can

00:14:19.326 --> 00:14:20.494 position:19% line:89% align:start
