00:14:20.628 --> 00:14:22.496 position:30% line:83% align:start
Lady Aileen is
the main character.

00:14:22.630 --> 00:14:24.865 position:13% line:83% align:start
Have a little bit of faith
in her, Grandmother!

00:14:24.998 --> 00:14:27.468 position:27% line:83% align:start
She won't lose in
a scenario this easy.

00:14:27.602 --> 00:14:28.902 position:38% line:89% align:start
Will you?

00:14:29.970 --> 00:14:31.472 position:33% line:89% align:start
Lady Aileen.

00:14:31.606 --> 00:14:34.776 position:19% line:83% align:start
What do you say you and
I have a little more fun?

00:14:34.908 --> 00:14:37.144 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
So she wants to play.

00:14:40.782 --> 00:14:42.282 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Of course, Lady Lilia.

00:14:42.416 --> 00:14:45.520 position:30% line:83% align:start
But know this:
it will be the last time.

00:14:45.653 --> 00:14:49.089 position:19% line:83% align:start
Yes, that's the spirit,
Lady Aileen.

00:14:49.223 --> 00:14:51.925 position:5% line:89% align:start
I would expect no less from you.

00:14:57.599 --> 00:14:58.733 position:30% line:89% align:start
[LILIA giggles]

00:14:58.867 --> 00:15:02.570 position:16% line:83% align:start
If this truly is reality,
isn't it quite cruel?

00:15:02.704 --> 00:15:04.304 position:27% line:89% align:start
Poor Lady Aileen!

00:15:06.173 --> 00:15:09.410 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CÃDRIC]
Lilia, are you sure about this?

00:15:09.544 --> 00:15:12.479 position:21% line:83% align:start
Huh? Are you worried
about something?

00:15:12.614 --> 00:15:13.947 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yes.

00:15:14.081 --> 00:15:16.483 position:13% line:83% align:start
The culprit who attacked my
brother is still out there.

00:15:16.618 --> 00:15:18.485 position:27% line:89% align:start
And what's more--

00:15:18.620 --> 00:15:21.656 position:16% line:83% align:start
[LILIA] Oh, is he worried
his more capable brother

00:15:21.790 --> 00:15:23.290 position:19% line:89% align:start
