00:15:23.424 --> 00:15:26.393 position:24% line:83% align:start
What an exhausting,
small-minded man.

00:15:26.528 --> 00:15:28.596 position:19% line:83% align:start
Your kindness is what
I love most about you,

00:15:28.730 --> 00:15:30.164 position:30% line:89% align:start
Prince CÃ©dric!

00:15:33.668 --> 00:15:36.203 position:21% line:83% align:start
Be wary of bowing to
a woman's beck and call.

00:15:36.336 --> 00:15:38.472 position:19% line:89% align:start
Sheep get boring fast.

00:15:44.111 --> 00:15:45.479 position:35% line:83% align:start
[BELZEBUTH]
Aileen.

00:15:47.749 --> 00:15:51.985 position:35% line:83% align:start
I beg you.
Please take care of my lord.

00:15:52.119 --> 00:15:53.621 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
I will.

00:15:54.656 --> 00:15:58.392 position:13% line:83% align:start
And don't you forget, I am
the demon lord's future wife.

00:16:00.895 --> 00:16:02.963 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
He's in there.

00:16:03.096 --> 00:16:04.331 position:21% line:89% align:start
Almond's a good bird.

00:16:04.465 --> 00:16:05.966 position:33% line:83% align:start
Wouldn't have
found it without him.

00:16:06.099 --> 00:16:09.036 position:19% line:83% align:start
It seems there's a holy
barrier to ward off outsiders.

00:16:09.169 --> 00:16:10.538 position:21% line:89% align:start
Child's play, I say.

00:16:10.672 --> 00:16:12.607 position:24% line:83% align:start
My sword can surely
break through that barrier

00:16:12.740 --> 00:16:13.775 position:35% line:89% align:start
with ease.

00:16:13.908 --> 00:16:15.777 position:27% line:83% align:start
I see they still
underestimate me.

00:16:15.910 --> 00:16:19.246 position:7% line:83% align:start
[ELEPHAS] Most people wouldn't
think about jumping off a cliff.

00:16:19.379 --> 00:16:20.782 position:24% line:89% align:start
Not at this height.

00:16:20.915 --> 00:16:22.149 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's time.

00:16:22.282 --> 00:16:24.886 position:27% line:83% align:start
Prepare your wind
magic while I tear down

00:16:25.018 --> 00:16:27.354 position:24% line:83% align:start
the "holy" barrier
with my sword.

00:16:27.488 --> 00:16:32.125 position:19% line:83% align:start
And may I remind you--
you'll be executed if caught.

00:16:32.259 --> 00:16:33.795 position:19% line:89% align:start
I'm well aware of that.

00:16:33.928 --> 00:16:35.395 position:24% line:89% align:start
As long as you are.

00:16:36.831 --> 00:16:38.065 position:35% line:89% align:start
Your hand.

00:16:44.204 --> 00:16:47.174 position:24% line:89% align:start
Zhuideze jeveonhwa.

00:16:51.345 --> 00:16:52.780 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Holy sword!

00:16:59.787 --> 00:17:01.288 position:21% line:89% align:start
It's most remarkable.

00:17:01.421 --> 00:17:03.625 position:27% line:83% align:start
The holy sword is
loyal to your hand.

00:17:03.758 --> 00:17:04.959 position:19% line:89% align:start
Yes, for now at least.

00:17:05.092 --> 00:17:06.528 position:27% line:83% align:start
