want to listen. Uh...

00:17:09.329 --> 00:17:10.732 position:30% line:89% align:start
[AILEEN yelps]

00:17:12.132 --> 00:17:14.034 position:38% line:83% align:start
[ELEPHAS]
Lady Aileen! Are you all right?

00:17:14.167 --> 00:17:15.402 position:24% line:89% align:start
Yes, more or less.

00:17:15.537 --> 00:17:17.104 position:24% line:83% align:start
And as you've just
seen, it feels like

00:17:17.237 --> 00:17:20.207 position:24% line:83% align:start
the holy sword has
a mind of its own--uh...

00:17:24.378 --> 00:17:26.046 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Prince CÃ©dric.

00:17:31.251 --> 00:17:34.187 position:21% line:83% align:start
I suppose you're here
to see my brother.

00:17:34.321 --> 00:17:35.723 position:24% line:89% align:start
Get off the ground.

00:17:35.857 --> 00:17:37.057 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Huh?

00:17:44.732 --> 00:17:47.769 position:13% line:83% align:start
That door over there leads
to my brother's bedroom.

00:17:47.902 --> 00:17:49.504 position:16% line:89% align:start
Go ahead, have your way.

00:17:49.637 --> 00:17:51.204 position:13% line:89% align:start
This better not be a trick.

00:17:51.338 --> 00:17:52.774 position:30% line:83% align:start
Do whatever you
need to and leave.

00:17:52.907 --> 00:17:54.742 position:13% line:83% align:start
And know that I won't save
you if you get caught

00:17:54.876 --> 00:17:56.443 position:30% line:89% align:start
by the guards.

00:18:02.249 --> 00:18:04.251 position:33% line:83% align:start
Stay here and
keep watch, Elephas.

00:18:11.893 --> 00:18:13.226 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Oh, my love!

00:18:20.668 --> 00:18:22.102 position:35% line:89% align:start
He's alive!

00:18:26.975 --> 00:18:28.442 position:30% line:89% align:start
Thank goodness.

00:18:28.576 --> 00:18:31.779 position:7% line:83% align:start
As long as he's still with me,
nothing else matters.

00:18:31.913 --> 00:18:33.347 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE]
Lilia?

00:18:39.386 --> 00:18:41.254 position:19% line:89% align:start
Who are you? Unhand me!

00:18:43.725 --> 00:18:45.325 position:21% line:83% align:start
After all we've been
through together,

00:18:45.459 --> 00:18:48.195 position:27% line:83% align:start
