can't recall who I am.

00:18:50.732 --> 00:18:53.500 position:13% line:83% align:start
Then I suppose there's no
other choice to make here.

00:18:53.635 --> 00:18:55.003 position:13% line:89% align:start
I know what I must do now!

00:18:55.135 --> 00:18:57.038 position:19% line:83% align:start
Lord Claude, you'd make
me the happiest woman

00:18:57.170 --> 00:18:58.338 position:24% line:89% align:start
if you married me!

00:18:58.472 --> 00:19:00.041 position:13% line:89% align:start
What are you talking about?

00:19:00.173 --> 00:19:01.576 position:7% line:89% align:start
All you have to do is say yes,

00:19:01.709 --> 00:19:03.477 position:19% line:83% align:start
and I can promise you a
comfortable, cushy life

00:19:03.611 --> 00:19:05.680 position:27% line:83% align:start
full of laughter,
love, and happiness!

00:19:05.813 --> 00:19:08.616 position:16% line:83% align:start
No need to be modest with
me, just take the plunge!

00:19:08.750 --> 00:19:11.218 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'm not so desperate that
I'd marry the first person

00:19:11.351 --> 00:19:13.253 position:27% line:83% align:start
to propose to me
without introduction,

00:19:13.387 --> 00:19:14.656 position:24% line:89% align:start
lost memory or no.

00:19:14.789 --> 00:19:16.824 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Oh! How rude of me.

00:19:18.425 --> 00:19:20.928 position:27% line:83% align:start
Hello, my name is
Aileen Lauren d'Autriche,

00:19:21.062 --> 00:19:25.700 position:16% line:83% align:start
and I happen to be your
fiancÃ©e, My Lord Claude.

00:19:25.833 --> 00:19:27.802 position:19% line:83% align:start
Are you the Aileen that
they warned me about?

00:19:27.935 --> 00:19:29.704 position:19% line:83% align:start
I've no desire to marry
someone like you,

00:19:29.837 --> 00:19:31.204 position:16% line:89% align:start
so please just leave me.

00:19:31.338 --> 00:19:32.540 position:35% line:89% align:start
Just leave?

00:19:32.674 --> 00:19:34.742 position:24% line:83% align:start
That's being a tad
cold, Lord Claude.

00:19:34.876 --> 00:19:37.177 position:27% line:83% align:start
I will not become
the demon lord again.

00:19:37.310 --> 00:19:39.413 position:21% line:83% align:start
I burdened my country
and my people

00:19:39.547 --> 00:19:41.849 position:33% line:83% align:start
